                <a data-m='{"pid":"tab","id":"nn3m2r5a2","sN":3,"aN":"m2r5a2"}' href="#" name="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-1-image coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-1-content" class="f-active" tabindex="0">学习</a>
    <a data-m='{"pid":"tab","id":"nn4m2r5a2","sN":4,"aN":"m2r5a2"}' href="#" name="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-2-image coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-2-content"  tabindex="1">书写</a>
    <a data-m='{"pid":"tab","id":"nn5m2r5a2","sN":5,"aN":"m2r5a2"}' href="#" name="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-3-image coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-3-content"  tabindex="2">画图</a>

        </div>
        <button data-m='{"pid":"next","id":"nn6m2r5a2","sN":6,"aN":"m2r5a2"}' tabindex="-1" class="c-flipper f-next" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="下一页" name="next"></button>
            <section id="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-1-content" role="tabpanel" aria-label="学习">
        
                <p class="c-paragraph" ><p>使用像OneNote这样的工具，可以帮助您计算数学方程式，从而处理每个任务并实现快速学习。</p></p>

        
    </section>
    <section id="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-2-content" role="tabpanel" aria-label="书写" aria-hidden="aria-hidden">
        
                <p class="c-paragraph" ><p>连接 Surface&nbsp;Go&nbsp;2 特制版键盘盖<sup>*</sup>，无论何时何地都能获得出色的打字体验——现有新颜色可选<sup>4</sup>，并带有可精确导航的集成玻璃触控板。</p>
</p>

        
    </section>
    <section id="coreui-multifeature-3f7fxbd-item-3-content" role="tabpanel" aria-label="画图" aria-hidden="aria-hidden">
        
                <p class="c-paragraph" ><p>使用 Surface 触控笔<sup>*</sup> 在屏幕上直接书写笔记、做作业、绘画、素描和上色。</p></p>

        
    </section>

